  </fragment>
  <Navigation />
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-container">
      <div class="hero-left">
        <div class="hero-badge fade-in-up">
          [ EXPERT PAPERLESS VALIDATION FOR PHARMA ]
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-title fade-in-up">
          GoVal Paperless Validation Solution.<br>
          Stay Compliant,<br>
          <span class="text-primary">Stay Ahead.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle fade-in-up">
          GoVal was founded on the principle that validation should be efficient, compliant, and accessible. Our platform is engineered for significant validation cost reduction, replacing expensive, paper-based systems with streamlined digital workflows. We revolutionize life sciences validation with a robust GxP Compliance Software suite designed for 21 CFR Part 11 and Annex 11, ensuring audit-ready documentation and data integrity from start to finish.<br />
          <br>With a team of validation and technology experts, we developed a robust GxP Compliance Software suite designed for 21 CFR Part 11 compliance and Annex 11 validation, delivering comprehensive pharmaceutical validation software. Our modular platform adapts to your workflow, ensuring seamless integration and scalable validation across all your systems. Experience faster audits and fewer errors with built-in best practices and real-time reporting. Our Risk-Based CSV methodology and VLMS software ensure audit-ready documentation and data integrity from requirements through execution.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-buttons fade-in-up">
          <a href="/contact-us" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
            <span>Get Started</span>
            <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-right">
        <div class="hero-image-container fade-in-up">
          <img 
            src="/images/web-bg-dis.webp" 
            alt="GoVal Digital Validation Platform - Pharma & Life Sciences Solutions" 
            class="hero-image"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="key-benefits-text fade-in-up">
        <p class="subtitle">[ KEY BENEFITS AT A GLANCE ]</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          Key Features of Our GAMP 5 Validation Software.
        </h2>
        <h3>Why Choose Our Digital Validation Platform Over Paper-Based Methods?</h3>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          As the best validation platform for life sciences, GoVal's digital system revolutionizes your entire process with a secure, paperless approach. Our clients achieve rapid GxP compliance through fully automated workflows and real-time, audit-ready data trails, ensuring both efficiency and 
          <br>robust data integrity.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3">
        <div class="card fade-in-up card-blue">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon blue">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Accelerated GxP Compliance Software</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-text">Automated workflows and real-time audit trails ensure fast and reliable compliance with regulatory standards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-in-up card-green">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon green">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">100% Paperless Validation Solutions</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-text">Eliminate manual processes and reduce errors with complete digital transformation of your validation workflows.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-in-up card-purple">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon purple">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Enhanced Audit Readiness</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-text">Our Risk-Based CSV workflows and validation automation platform automate audit trails and reports, enabling enterprise validation platform capabilities.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card fade-in-up card-orange">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon orange">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Continuous Validation</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-text">Integrate validation into your CI/CD pipeline. GoVal supports DevOps agility with automated regression testing and scheduled periodic reviews, ensuring a constant state of control.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-in-up card-teal">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon teal">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Validation Workflow Automation</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-text">Automate document routing, reviews, and e-signatures. Our platform enforces 21 CFR Part 11 compliant workflows, reducing manual handoffs and accelerating validation cycles.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-in-up card-pink">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon pink">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 1.105.895 2 2 2h12c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2V7M4 7h16M4 7v-.5c0-1.105.895-2 2-2h12c1.105 0 2 .895 2 2v.5m-16 4h16m-16 4h16"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Hybrid Validation Deployment</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-text">Blend traditional CSV rigor with modern CSA flexibility. Our risk-based platform lets you apply the right validation strategy for each system, optimizing effort while guaranteeing GxP compliance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card fade-in-up card-red">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon red">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Secure Data Integrity in Validation Lifecycle Management</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-text">Cloud-based platform with robust data management and security protocols ensuring data integrity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-in-up card-yellow">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon yellow">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">CFR Part 11 & Annex 11 Compliance</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-text">Built on GAMP 5 validation software principles for risk-based approach. Built-in tools for regulatory adherence and global compliance standards across all regions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-in-up card-indigo">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon indigo">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Productivity Improvement with our VLMS software</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-text">Optimize workflows and enhance efficiency across your validation processes with intelligent automation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section bg-gradient-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">
          GoVal AI - Take the Advantage of AI power
        </h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Experience the next generation of validation with Artificial Intelligence (AI) driving efficiency, accuracy, and compliance.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
        <a href="/goval-ai" class="btn btn-ai-blue btn-lg" aria-label="Explore GoVal AI">
          <span>Explore GoVal AI</span>
          <img src="/images/ai-stars.png" alt="AI Icon" class="ai-icon" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-container">
        <h2 class="cta-title">
          Ready to Transform Your Validation Process?
        </h2>
        <p class="cta-subtitle">
          Join leading pharma and other life sciences companies that rely on GoVal for digital validation—paperless VLMS, EDC, and Part 11/Annex 11–ready workflows that keep you audit-ready.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact-us" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
          Book a Demo
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  /* CSS Variables */
  :root {
    --blue-primary: #000000;
    --gray-900: #111827;
    --gray-700: #374151;
    --gray-600: #4b5563;
  }
  /* Global White Background */
  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  html, body {
    background: #ffffff;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  /* Hero Section - Clean White Background */
  .hero {
    background: #fcfcfc;
    padding: 5rem 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hero-container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 600px;
  }
  /* Left Side - Hero Content */
  .hero-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .hero-badge {
    background: rgba(248, 248, 248, 0.1);
    color: var(--blue-primary);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    width: fit-content;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .text-primary {
    color: var(--blue-primary);
  }
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    max-width: 85%;
  }
  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
  }
  /* Right Side - Hero Image */
  .hero-right {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hero-image-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-width: 550px;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: contrast(1.1) brightness(1.05) saturate(1.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .hero-image:hover {
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }
  /* Sections with White Background */
  .section {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }
  .bg-light {
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }
  .bg-gradient-section {
    background: #f5f5f5;
    color: #000000;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  /* AI section title override */
  .bg-gradient-section .section-title {
    color: #000000;
  }
  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  /* AI section subtitle override */
  .bg-gradient-section .section-subtitle {
    color: #666666;
  }
  /* AI Decoration Image */
  .ai-decoration {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
    vertical-align: middle;
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    background-color: #f5f5f5; /* Match container background */
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 4px;
  }
  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { 
      transform: translateY(0px);
    }
    50% { 
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
  }
  /* Grid System */
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .grid-cols-1 {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .grid-cols-2 {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
  .grid-cols-3 {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  }
  /* Cards */
  .card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }
  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .card-icon {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  /* Custom card colors */
  .card-icon.blue { background: #3b82f6; } /* Original */
  .card-icon.green { background: #10b981; } /* Original */
  .card-icon.purple { background: #8b5cf6; } /* Original */
  .card-icon.orange { background: #f97316; } /* New Color 1 */
  .card-icon.teal { background: #14b8a6; } /* New Color 2 */
  .card-icon.pink { background: #ec4899; } /* New Color 3 */
  .card-icon.red { background: #ef4444; } /* Original */
  .card-icon.yellow { background: #f59e0b; } /* Original */
  .card-icon.indigo { background: #6366f1; } /* Original */

  .card-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    margin: 0;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .card-text {
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.6;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  /* Card Hover Effects */
  .card.card-blue:hover { background: #3b82f6; }
  .card.card-green:hover { background: #10b981; }
  .card.card-purple:hover { background: #8b5cf6; }
  .card.card-orange:hover { background: #f97316; } /* New hover color */
  .card.card-teal:hover { background: #14b8a6; } /* New hover color */
  .card.card-pink:hover { background: #ec4899; } /* New hover color */
  .card.card-red:hover { background: #ef4444; }
  .card.card-yellow:hover { background: #f59e0b; }
  .card.card-indigo:hover { background: #6366f1; }

  .card:hover .card-icon {
    background: white;
    color: #374151;
  }
  .card:hover .card-title,
  .card:hover .card-text {
    color: white;
  }
  
  /* Key Benefits Section Styles */
  .key-benefits-text {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
  }
  /* Add space below the subtitle in the "Why Choose GoVal" section */
  .section-subtitle {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .subtitle {
    color: #000000;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #111827;
  }
  .highlight {
    color: #2563eb;
  }
  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-container {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: rgb(253, 251, 251);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }
  .cta-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .cta-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  /* Buttons */
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    position: relative;
